title: Carter G. Woodson Home National Historic Site: Our Staff & Offices
body: Explore This Park    Learn About the Park     Management     Our Staff & Offices              Our Staff & Offices       Joy Kinard is the District Manager responsible for the Carter G. Woodson Home NHS, as well as the Mary McLeod Bethune Council House NHS and the Capitol Hill Parks. The staffs of National Capital Parks-East and the Mary McLeod Bethune Council House NHS provide support for the Carter G. Woodson Home NHS as necessary. For information contact: Carter G. Woodson Home NHS c/o Mary McLeod Bethune Council House NHS 1318 Vermont Avenue, NW Washington, DC 2005-3607 (202) 673-2402
